# Netlify security headers — applied to the ERP at app.isheekaevents.com.
# Safe set (no breakage risk). A Content-Security-Policy is intentionally left out
# here because it must be tested against Supabase/PWA calls before enabling — see
# the commented template at the bottom; add it under /* once verified.
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(self)
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin

